T1  - The Order-Dependent Luce Model
AU  - Tserenjigmid, Gerelt
Y1  - 2021/02/25
PY  - 2021
DA  - 2021/11/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2020.3866
DO  - 10.1287/mnsc.2020.3866
T2  - Management Science
